message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been highly valued by many satisfied customers. I believe it would be a great addition to your collection and enhance your experience. Considering its quality and the benefits it provides, I am offering it to you at a special introductory price of $95. This is a unique opportunity to acquire a product worth more to you than its cost, making it a valuable investment. I look forward to hearing your decision.
